  "detailed_description": "<strong>Survive in a decaying world: </strong><br>Where it is rumored a group of sorcerers accidentally unleashed chaos, <br>and where misery and despair seem to be all that flourishes.<br>It may <u>seem</u> this realm is incurable.<br><br><strong> Features: </strong><br>*Crafting and building.<br>*Spells that consume reagents.<br>*Simple Farming<br>*Caves, creatures and treasure.<br>*Action based skill system with no classes.<br>*Become a ghost upon death and explore the spirit dimension.<br>*A very interactable world.<br>*Day, night and seasons.<br><br>Explore and build a home. All items save their place in the world,<br>So you can decorate your home however you like. Take down many<br>creatures for loot or food.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Survive in a decaying world: </strong><br>Where it is rumored a group of sorcerers accidentally unleashed chaos, <br>and where misery and despair seem to be all that flourishes.<br>It may <u>seem</u> this realm is incurable.<br><br><strong> Features: </strong><br>*Crafting and building.<br>*Spells that consume reagents.<br>*Simple Farming<br>*Caves, creatures and treasure.<br>*Action based skill system with no classes.<br>*Become a ghost upon death and explore the spirit dimension.<br>*A very interactable world.<br>*Day, night and seasons.<br><br>Explore and build a home. All items save their place in the world,<br>So you can decorate your home however you like. Take down many<br>creatures for loot or food.",
